## Project Scope

This project is designed to:
- Analyze user text sentiment.
- Classify text as Positive, Negative, or Neutral.
- Demonstrate the basics of Natural Language Processing (NLP).
- Serve as a beginner-friendly AI and Python project.
- Help understand sentiment analysis techniques used in real-world applications.

---

## Features

- Analyze text sentiment instantly.
- Displays sentiment polarity score.
- Classifies text into Positive, Negative, or Neutral.
- Simple and easy-to-use command-line interface.
- Lightweight and beginner-friendly project.

---

## Technologies Used

- Python 3
- TextBlob
- Natural Language Processing (NLP)


## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AI-Sentiment-Analyzer.git
```

2. Install the required library:

```bash
pip install textblob
```

3. Run the project:

```bash
python sentiment_analyzer.py
```

